        LETTER          = LETTER + "ÀÁÂÃÄÅÆÇÈÉÊËÌÍÎÏÐÑÒÓÔÕÖØÙÚÛÜÝÞßàáâãäåæçèéêëìíîïðñòóôõöøùúûüýþÿ";
	SUFFIX		= ANY - SP - HT - VT - NL ;
	HEAD		= SUFFIX - "{%\\()[]|" ;
--      OP		= HEAD - LETTER - DIGIT ;

Tokens
        Comments        = {-SP | -HT | -VT | -NL | -("%" {ANY} EOL&TRUE) |
			   "{" @Reset(0)
			       {
			         "{"&True @Incr(0) |
				 "}"&Is_Set(0) @Decr(0) |
				 ^"{}"
			       }*
			   "}"
			  }+ ; 
                        Priority Shift > Reduce;

-- Le "\" est un caractère d'échappement pour "()[]|"
        %word           = (-"\\" SUFFIX | HEAD) {-"\\" SUFFIX | HEAD}* ;
                        Priority Shift > Reduce;

